 the others became over 75% full\" href=\"http://www.geekspeak.co.nz/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/vrobbers-5.jpg\" rel=\"gallery1\"><img class=\"alignnone size-thumbnail wp-image-541\" alt=\"vrobbers-5\" src=\"http://www.geekspeak.co.nz/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/vrobbers-5-200x200.jpg\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" /></a><a class=\"fancybox\" title=\"Amongst the users we hid gang members with large amounts of money to be stolen from\" href=\"http://www.geekspeak.co.nz/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/vrobbers7.jpg\" rel=\"gallery1\"><img class=\"alignnone size-thumbnail wp-image-542\" alt=\"vrobbers7\" src=\"http://www.geekspeak.co.nz/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/vrobbers7-200x200.jpg\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" /></a><a class=\"fancybox\" title=\"To steal money off other people the users had to win a mini game\" href=\"http://www.geekspeak.co.nz/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/vrobbers-6.jpg\" rel=\"gallery1\"><img class=\"alignnone size-thumbnail wp-image-543\" alt=\"vrobbers-6\" src=\"http://www.geekspeak.co.nz/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/vrobbers-6-200x200.jpg\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" /></a><a class=\"fancybox\" title=\"The mini game was disarming the alarm within a certain time period by clipping wires in the right order\" href=\"http://www.geekspeak.co.nz/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/vrobbers-8.jpg\" rel=\"gallery1\"><img class=\"alignnone size-thumbnail wp-image-544\" alt=\"vrobbers-8\" src=\"http://www.geekspeak.co.nz/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/vrobbers-8-200x200.jpg\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" /></a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>Goals</h3>\r\nThe aim of this project was to increase sales by creating a fun game to drive prize giveaways rather than a simple entry mechanic.\r\n<h3>Technology</h3>\r\nThis project was built in Flash with the API built on the Zend Framework.\r\n<h3>Challenges</h3>\r\nThe main challenge around this project was security. Given the fact that there was $100,000 for prizes up for grabs it was important to stop any cheating.\r\n<h3>Solutions</h3>\r\nIll post the solutions to the security challenges once the campaign ends.\r\n<h3>Results</h3>\r\nThis project is still running but is doing very well. The game is simple, challenging and addictive.\r\n<h3></h3>', 'V Robbers', 'The aim of this project was to increase sales by creating a fun game to drive prize giveaways rather than a simple entry mechanic. ', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '533-revision-11', '', '', '2013-02-27 17:14:40', '2013-02-27 05:14:40', '', '533', 'http://www.geekspeak.co.nz/articles/533-revision-11/', '0', 'revision', '', '0'), ('660', '1', '2013-02-28 12:13:53', '2013-02-28 00:13:53', 'This is a site dedicated to writing better code through sharing tricks and tips I\'ve learned along my journey. I\'ll be trying to cover a broad spectrum from the basics to the complex and everything in between.\r\n<br /><br />\r\nIf you have any specific problems that you\'d like me to cover in an article, feel free to drop me a message on the contact page and I\'ll either point you to some resources or write it up for all to see.', 'Welcome to Geekspeak', 'Geekspeak is a site dedicated to writing better code through sharing tricks and tips', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '240-revision-26', '', '', '2013-02-28 12:13:53', '2013-02-28 00:13:53', '', '240', 'http://www.geekspeak.co.nz/articles/240-revision-26/', '0', 'revision', '', '0'), ('615', '1', '2013-02-28 12:08:08', '2013-02-28 00:08:08', 'This is a site dedicated to writing better code through sharing tricks and tips. I\'ll be writing articles on things which I\'ve found useful, hard to find solutions to, custom solutions I\'ve made, code snippets or anything i find interesting really. I\'ll be trying to cover everything from the basics to the complex and everything in between.\r\n<br /><br />\r\nPlease bear with me while i start to build my article base.\r\n<br /><br />\r\nIf you have any specific problems that you\'d like me to cover in an article, feel free to drop me a message on the contact p